comment: /**  * Encodes the key before its sent as a {@link javax.jms.Message} message.  *  * @param key  the original key  * @return the encoded key  */
code: /**  * Encodes the key before its sent as a {@link javax.jms.Message} message.  *  * @param key  the original key  * @return the encoded key  */ String encodeKey(String key).

comment: /**  * Decodes the key after its received from a {@link javax.jms.Message} message.  *  * @param key the encoded key  * @return the decoded key as the original key  */
code: /**  * Decodes the key after its received from a {@link javax.jms.Message} message.  *  * @param key the encoded key  * @return the decoded key as the original key  */ String decodeKey(String key).
